%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-5g-wireless-technology-shaping-our-world-2023-7%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%3E5G%20Playbook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20one%20of%20our%20time's%20most%20important%20tech%20innovations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video-game%20industry%20is%20a%20behemoth%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2022%2F07%2Fgaming-pandemic-lockdowns-pwc-growth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20estimate%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20could%20grow%20to%20be%20worth%20more%20than%20%24320%20billion%20this%20decade.%20So%20it's%20little%20wonder%20that%20it's%20adopting%205G%20as%20a%20cornerstone%20technology%20of%20its%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-frequency-is-5g%5C%22%3Etechnology%20that%20powers%20mobile%20broadband%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20now%205G%20is%20being%20used%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20delivery%20of%20games%20to%20end%20players%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20reduce%20latency%20within%20mobile%20games%2C%20allowing%20higher-quality%20graphics%20games%20to%20be%20played%20on%20mobile%20hardware%2C%20which%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20just%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20It's%20also%20kick-starting%20the%20cloud-gaming%20revolution%20%E2%80%94%20removing%20the%20need%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20physical%20gaming%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%2C%20significant%20change%20in%20having%205G%20technology%20for%20people%20is%20obviously%20that%20it's%20faster%20and%20more%20stable%20internet%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhavina%20Bharkhada%2C%20the%20head%20of%20communications%20and%20campaigns%20at%20Ukie%2C%20the%20trade%20body%20for%20the%20UK%20gaming%20industry%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20available%2C%205G%20offers%20users%20higher%20data-transfer%20speeds%20and%20lower%20latency%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20make%20playing%20games%20so%20much%20more%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharkhada%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20latency%20of%205G%20makes%20a%20consequential%20difference%20for%20gamers%20when%20they're%20tasked%20with%20making%20split-second%20decisions%20on%20where%20to%20shoot%20and%20what%20to%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLow%20latency%20is%20absolutely%20crucial%20to%20all%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20faster%20internet%2C%20better%20connection%20speeds%2C%20and%20improved%20connections%20come%20a%20better%20gaming%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Whatley%2C%20the%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20the%20gaming-creative%20agency%20Diva%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20offers%20a%20revolution%20in%20gaming%20because%20of%20the%20simple%20advance%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20Whatley%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BMore%20data%20packets%20can%20be%20exchanged%20at%20speed%2C%20meaning%20higher-quality%20output%20of%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMobile%20and%20cloud%20gaming%20could%20see%20the%20most%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Whatley%2C%20there%20are%20real%20opportunities%20for%20so-called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAAA_(video_game_industry)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAAA%20game%20studios%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20huge%20companies%20that%20release%20household%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20genuine%20benefit%20of%205G%20is%20the%20enablement%20of%20AAA%20game-streaming%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20boot%20up%20the%20latest%20AAA%20release%20and%20stream%20to%20your%20handheld%20or%20console%20device%20at%20high%20definition%20and%2For%204K%20instantly%20is%20only%20really%20enabled%20by%205G%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloud%20gaming%2C%20where%20you%20can%20play%20games%20hosted%20in%20remote%20data%20centers%20without%20owning%20any%20physical%20game%20disc%20or%20cartridge%2C%20has%20become%20a%20major%20growth%20area%20for%20the%20industry.%20Research%20from%20the%20tech%20provider%20Ericsson%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ericsson.com%2Fen%2Freports-and-papers%2Fmobility-report%2Farticles%2F5g-opportunities-in-the-cloud-gaming-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E35%20services%20launched%20cloud-gaming%20platforms%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20more%20expected%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20longest-standing%20cloud-gaming%20platforms%20is%20Xbox%20Cloud%20Gaming%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20by%20Microsoft%20in%202019.%20Whatley%20said%20he%20believed%20that%20the%20success%20of%20Xbox%20Cloud%20Gaming%20was%20dependent%20on%20the%20rollout%20of%205G%20technology%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20technology%20allows%20players%20to%20game%20not%20only%20on%20their%20home%20consoles%20but%20also%20on%20mobile%20devices.%20In%20previous%20years%2C%20that%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20because%20of%20slow%20internet%20speeds%20and%20the%20high%20data%20volumes%20required%20to%20render%20graphics%20and%20send%20and%20receive%20information%20about%20player%20movements.%20But%20with%205G's%20superfast%20internet%20speeds%2C%20it's%20possible%20to%20mimic%20the%20console%20experience%20wherever%20you%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBharkhada%20said%20cloud%20gaming%20would%20be%20a%20driver%20of%20the%20gaming%20sector%3A%20%26quot%3B5G%20is%20going%20to%20be%20really%2C%20really%20important%20because%20more%20players%20can%20connect%20to%20each%20other%20in%20that%20multiplayer%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%205G%20is%20mostly%20used%20in%20mobile%20games%20but%20set%20to%20soon%20be%20used%20for%20cloud%20and%20streaming%20services%20when%20it%20becomes%20more%20widely%20available%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20new%20gaming%20use%20case%3A%20augmented-%20and%20virtual-reality%20headsets.%20The%20release%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-eyesight-apple-vision-pro-how-it-works-2023-6%5C%22%3EApple%20Vision%20Pro%20in%20early%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20kick-start%20a%20race%20for%20superfast%2C%20immersive%20games%20using%20the%20headset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuddenly%2C%20that%20technology%20can%20be%20used%20by%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharkhada%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20opens%20up%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20opportunities%20that%20we've%20probably%20not%20had.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChanges%20in%20gaming%20could%20trickle%20down%20to%20other%20industries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%20in%20the%20games%20industry%20often%20trickles%20down%20to%20the%20wider%20world%20in%20time.%20Some%20TV%20productions%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20use%20the%20Unreal%20Engine%2C%20a%20game-rendering%20service%2C%20to%20produce%20real-time%203D%20graphics%20for%20sports%20analysis.%20Given%20that%2C%20Bharkhada%20said%20she%20believed%20that%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20mobile%20and%20cloud%20gaming%20would%20also%20have%20positive%20effects%20on%20industries%20that%20borrowed%20elements%20from%20the%20gaming%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20games%20are%20used%20as%20virtual%20training%20platforms%20for%20industries%20where%20the%20cost%20of%20real-world%20training%20is%20prohibitive%2C%20and%205G%20can%20help%20enable%20that.%20Also%2C%20the%20promise%20of%20immersive%20gaming%20through%20headsets%20could%20act%20as%20a%20test%20bed%20for%20real-world%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20that%20technology%20and%20testing%20it%20in%20our%20sector%20to%20then%20deploy%20across%20other%20sectors%2C%20I%20think%2C%20could%20be%20really%20beneficial%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharkhada%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-game-experts-5g-ne