icted%20a%20collapse%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20pointing%20to%20parties%20with%20disparate%20ideologies%20that%20have%20been%20sworn%20enemies%20in%20states%20for%20decades.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Puri%2C%20who%20handles%20the%20Petroleum%20and%20housing%20ministries%2C%20said%20the%20new%20front%20will%20%26quot%3Bcollapse%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20its%20own%20contradictions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20is%20a%20new%20arrival%2C%20a%20political%20start-up.%20They%20were%20born%20of%20an%20agitation%20against%20entrenched%20corruption.%20Today%20they%20want%20to%20tie%20up%20with%20someone%20who%20defined%20the%20entrenched%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%2C%20without%20naming%20the%20Congress.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20be%20in%20a%20similar%20quandary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trinamool%20will%20be%20unlikely%20to%20be%20happy%20with%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20or%20CPM%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20are%20not%20likely%20to%20be%20happy%20with%20the%20alliance%20in%20Delhi%20or%20Punjab...%20And%20I%20can%20go%20on%20giving%20these%20examples%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20criticizing%20the%20new%20Opposition%20front%20since%20it%20was%20announced%20last%20month%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20being%20old%20wine%20in%20new%20bottle.%20Several%20leaders%20have%20also%20predicted%20its%20collapse%2C%20pointing%20to%20its%20inner%20contradictions.%20The%20Opposition%20claims%20it%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20the%20ruling%20party's%20nervousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20of%20the%20BJP's%20own%20big%20pitch%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20exudes%20confidence%20and%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20roadmap%20for%202030%20and%202047%2C%20it%20is%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bempirical%2