derway%20on%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitendra%20Singh%20Bisen%2C%20chief%20of%20Vishwa%20Vedic%20Sanatan%20Sangh%2C%20has%20written%20an%20open%20letter%20inviting%20the%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20sides%20to%20hold%20talks%20to%20settle%20the%20Gyanvapi%20complex%20dispute%20with%20mutual%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBisen%20said%20that%20the%20letter%20has%20been%20issued%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Hindu%20side%20after%20the%20consent%20of%20Rakhi%20Singh%2C%20the%20main%20litigant%20in%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20matter%20can%20be%20resolved%20by%20mutual%20consent%2C%20then%20nothing%20can%20be%20better%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBisen%20in%20his%20letter%20said%20some%20anti-social%20elements%20want%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20this%20constitutional%20fight%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20for%20their%20personal%20gains%20which%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20harmful%20for%20both%2C%20the%20country%20and%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20all%20of%20us%20to%20set%20an%20example%20by%20settling%20this%20dispute%20peacefully%20through%20mutual%20dialogue%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20our%20country%20and%20society%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20that%20a%20peaceful%20solution%20can%20be%20found%20outside%20the%20court%20in%20the%20above%20matter%20by%20mutual%20discussion.%20We%20welcome%20all%20of%20you%20to%20this%20dialogue%20with%20an%20open%20and%20pure%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoint%20Secretary%20of%20Intezamia%20Masjid%20Committee%2C%20Mohammad%20Yasin%20said%20the%20committee%20has%20received%20the%20letter%20and%20it%20will%20be%20deliberated%20upon%20in%20a%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20received%20the%20letter%20through%20the%20media.%20The%20letter%20will%20be%20presented%