20to%20confront%20Dhoni%20after%20the%20match%20to%20ask%20him%20about%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20this%20year%2C%20I%20was%20batting%20and%20I%20played%20a%20shot%20and%20got%20out%20at%20short%20third%20man.%20I%20turned%20around%20and%20saw%20'He%20is%20standing%20wrong.%20That's%20not%20where%20a%20fielder%20stands.%20He%20is%20standing%20at%20a%20wrong%20position%3B%20he%20should%20be%20more%20to%20the%20right.%20Then%20I%20realised%20'Oh'.%20I%20asked%20him%20after%20the%20match%2C%20'Bhaiyya%2C%20kyu%3F'%20(Why%3F)%20He%20said%20the%20way%20the%20ball%20was%20leaving%20my%20bat%3B%20the%20fielders%20should%20be%20a%20lot%20fine.%20Then%20I%20was%20like%20'WOW!%20I%20never%20even%20thought%20like%20that.%20To%20think%20so%20quickly%20then%20and%20there%2C%20and%20to%20understand%20the%20angle%20-%20cricket%20is%20all%20about%20angles%20-%20to%20read%20it%20is%20I%20think%20his%20biggest%20strength%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20all-rounder%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692295320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvj358518_venkatesh-iyer_625x300_17_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkolkata-knight-riders-star-venkatesh-iyer-recreates-viral-video-of-non-strike-batter-irritating-bowler-watch-4306262%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20social%20media%20is%20a%20gold-mine%20of%20content.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20funny%20to%20the%20core.%20One%20such%20video%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20is%20that%20of%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20star%20Venkatesh%20Iyer%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkolkata-knight-riders-star-venkatesh-iyer-recreates-viral-video-of-non-strike-batter-irritating-bowler-watch-4306262%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkolkata-knight-riders-