Chambal%20zone.%20There%20are%2014%20faces%20who%20lost%20the%20elections%20in%202018%2C%20including%207%20former%20ministers%20--%20Achal%20Sonkar%2C%20Nanaji%20Mohad%2C%20Omprakash%20Dhurve%2C%20Aidal%20Singh%20Kansana%2C%20Nirmala%20Bhuria%2C%20Lalita%20Yadav%2C%20and%20Lal%20Singh%20Arya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20congratulated%20the%20candidates.%20%26quot%3BFulfill%20the%20trust%20that%20the%20party%20has%20reposed%20on%20all%20of%20you%20and%20emerge%20victorious%2C%20best%20wishes%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20tweet%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Gohad%20reserve%20seat%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20given%20ticket%20to%20Scheduled%20Caste%20Morcha%20national%20president%20Lal%20Singh%20Arya%20instead%20of%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20loyalist%20Ranveer%20Jatav.%20Mr%20Singh%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20stronger%20candidate%20locally%20--%20being%20a%20former%20minister%2C%20and%20the%20party's%20national%20in-charge%20of%20the%20SC%20Morcha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Congress's%20Ranveer%20Jatav%20won%20by%20defeating%20Mr%20Arya%2C%20and%20later%20joined%20the%20BJP%20with%20Mr%20Scindia.%20But%20he%20lost%20the%202020%20by-election%2C%20after%20which%20the%20party%20made%20him%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Handcrafts%20Development%20Corporation%20and%20gave%20him%20the%20status%20of%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20but%20cut%20off%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20list%2C%20though%2C%20includes%20many%20names%20that%20have%20been%20embroiled%20in%20controversies.%20The%20list%20includes%20Dhruv%20Narayan%20Singh%2C%20the%20candidate%20for%20the%20Bhopal%20Central%20Assembly.%20Dhruv%20Narayan%20Singh%20was%20a%20suspect%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20RTI%20activist%20Shehla%20Masood.%20Two%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20relatives%20of%20Shehla%20Masood%20demanded%20a%20re-inquiry%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritam%20Singh%20Lodhi%20has%20been%20made%20the%20candidate%20from%20Pichor%20assembly%20seat%20in%20Shivpuri%20district.%20Pichor%20is%20the%20invincible%20fort%20of%20KP%20Singh%20%26quot%3BKakkaju%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Congress.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20party%20suspended%20Pritam%20Singh%20Lodhi%20over%20his%20statement%20about%20Brahmins.%20This%20is%20the%20third%20time%20Pritam%20Singh%20Lodhi%20will%20go%20toe-to-toe%20against%20%26quot%3BKakkaju%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20candidates%20are%20also%20members%20of%20political%20families%20--%20Sarla%20Rawat%2C%20daughter-in-law%20of%20former%20Sabalgarh%20MLA%20Meharban%20Singh%20Rawat%2C%20Virendra%20Singh%20Lodhi%2C%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Damoh%20MP%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Lodhi%2C%20Neeraj%20Singh%2C%20son%20of%20ex-MLA%20Pratibha%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lodhi%20has%20been%20nominated%20from%20the%20Banda%20assembly%20seat%20in%20Sagar%2C%20which%20has%20around%2050%2C000%20voters%20belonging%20to%20the%20Lodhi%20community.%20Currently%20Congress's%20Tarwar%20Singh%20Lodhi%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20Banda.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamakhya%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20son%20of%20ex-MLA%20Manvendra%20Singh%2C%20has%20got%20the%20ticket%20from%20Maharajpur%20in%20Chhatarpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692295140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F708qgjb8_bjp-central-committee-meeting-1200_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh-bjp-covers-backward-community-seats-first-4307169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20released%20the%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20elections%2C%20in%20which%2021%20names%20have%20been%20announced%20from%20the%20first%20and%2039%20from%20the%20second.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-ch