f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1691855958593667112%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20post%20from%20Starlink's%20official%20X%20account%20noted%20that%20more%20than%20650%20satellite%20internet%20kits%20have%20been%20shipped%20to%20over%2040%20organizations%20that%20are%20helping%20recovery%20efforts%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20Starlink%20team%20covered%20expedited%20shipping%20and%20distribution%20costs%20for%20all%20kits%20delivered%20to%20recovery%20efforts%20in%20Maui%2C%20donated%20~35%25%20of%20the%20hardware%20costs%2C%20and%20we%20are%20working%20with%20local%20retailers%20to%20make%20Starlink%20available%20below%20cost.%20More%20to%20come%20as%20needed!''%20another%20tweet%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETo%20help%20provide%20connectivity%20in%20Maui%2C%20the%20Starlink%20team%20has%20shipped%20and%20distributed%20more%20than%20650%20kits%20to%2040%2B%20organizations%20on%20the%20island%20supporting%20recovery%20efforts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FnO62ihDxx5%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FnO62ihDxx5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Starlink%20(%40Starlink)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStarlink%2Fstatus%2F1691864666983768504%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20organizations%20is%20Red%20Lightning%20Disaster%20Relief%2C%20which%20said%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20it%20bought%2020%20Starlink%20systems%20and%20has%20begun%20setting%20them%20up%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Ftechnology%2Felon-musk-says-spacex-using-starlink-aid-maui-wildfire-recovery%5C%22%3EFox%20Business.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Red%20Link%20further%20noted%20that%C2%A0communication%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20needs%20in%20many%20areas%20with%20power%20lines%20down%20and%20connectivity%20hard%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20provides%20internet%20service%20through%20a%20network%20of%20satellites%20in%20low%20Earth%20orbit%2C%20and%20its%20kits%20include%20pre-connected%20equipment%20for%20easy%20installation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wildfires%20in%20Maui%20are%20the%20deadliest%20the%20United%20States%20has%20seen%20in%20over%20100%20years.%20At%20least%20106%20people%20have%20been%20reported%20dead%2C%20and%20over%201%2C300%20people%20are%20still%20missing.%20The%20fires%20also%20destroyed%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0Amazon%20Executive%20Chairman%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeff-bezos-lauren-sanchez-donate-100-million-to-help-rebuild-maui-after-devastating-wildfire-4295293%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos%C2%A0and%20fiance%20Lauren%20Sanchez%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20also%20pledged%20to%20donate%20%24100%20million%20to%20help%20rebuild%20Maui.%20Ms.%20Sanchez%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20announce%20that%20she%20and%20the%20former%20Amazon%20CEO%20are%20''heartbroken''%20by%20the%20destruction%20and%20are%20creating%20a%20fund%20to%20help%20the%20Hawaiian%20island%20''get%20back%20on%20its%20feet.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maui%20wildfire%2C%20which%20started%20August%208%2C%20burned%20through%20more%20than%202%2C500%20acres%20across%20historic%20towns%20like%20Lahaina.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20known%20to%20have%20died%20in%20the%20horrific%20wildfire%20reached%20106%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20authorities%20said%2C%20as%20a%20makeshift%20morgue%20was%20expanded%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20tragedy%2C%20AFP%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wildfire%20is%20the%20deadliest%20in%20the%20United%20States%20since%201918%2C%20when%20453%20people%20died%20in%20Minnesota%20and%20Wisconsin%2C%20according%20to%20the%20nonprofit