edly%20committing%20blasphemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fchurches-vandalised-in-pakistans-punjab-province-over-blasphemy-allegations-535431%5C%22%3Eseveral%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fpakistan-arrests-129-muslims-after-mob-attacks-on-churches-and-homes-of-minority-christians%2Farticle67205469.ece%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20local%20Muslims%20accused%20Raja%20Amir%20and%20his%20friend%20of%20desecrating%20the%20Holy%20Quran%20and%20making%20objectionable%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20both%20hailed%20from%20the%20Cinema%20Basti%20area%2C%20a%20Christian%20colony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20announcement%20was%20made%20from%20the%20Mehtab%20Mosque%2C%20where%20a%20man%20was%20seen%20inciting%20locals%20through%20a%20loudspeaker%2C%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20fight%20against%20those%20who%20desecrated%20the%20holy%20%3Cem%3EQuran%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20you%20sit%20and%20eat%20at%20your%20homes%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20mob%20attacked%20the%20area%20and%20burnt%20churches%20and%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20arrested%20Raja%20Amir%20under%20sections%20295%20B%20and%20C%20for%20purportedly%20desecrating%20the%20holy%20%3Cem%3EQuran%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20writing%20derogatory%20remarks%20about%20the%20Prophet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20who%20made%20the%20announcement%20from%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20mob.%20According%20to%20the%20locals%2C%20religious%20extremist%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20Jamaat-Ahle-Sunnat%20and%20Tehreek-i-Labbaik%20Pakistan%20led%20the%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Peter%20Jacob%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20executive%20director%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Justice%2C%20said%20that%20the%20alleged%20blasphemous%20paper%20had%20the%20accused%E2%80%99s%20picture%20attached%20to%20it%2C%20which%20raises%20suspicions.%20He%20questioned%20how%20someone%20would%20commit%20a%20crime%20and%20then%20leave%20behind%20evidence%20of%20his%20or%20her%20identity.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20pattern%20has%20been%20seen%20in%20cases%20such%20as%20in%20Shanti%20Nagar%20in%201997%2C%20Sangla%20Hill%20in%202005%2C%20Gojra%20and%20Korian%20in%202009%2C%20and%20many%20other%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRaja%20Amir%20Masih%2C%20who%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20committed%20blasphemy%2C%20is%20illiterate%20and%20works%20as%20a%20sanitation%20worker%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jaranwala%20tragedy%20has%20left%20numerous%20Christians%20homeless%20and%20instilled%20fear%20among%20religious%20minorities%20throughout%20the%20nation.%20The%20places%20of%20worship%20that%20had%20once%20provided%20solace%20for%20the%20Christian%20community%20were%20reduced%20to%20ashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarhatullah%20Babar%2C%20former%20senator%20and%20president%20of%20PPP%E2%80%99s%20Human%20Rights%20Cell%2C%20condemned%20the%20incident%20and%20said%20that%20there%20are%20disturbing%20reports%20on%20social%20media%20of%20churches%20being%20desecrated%20in%20Jaranwala%2C%20Faisalabad.%20He%20added%20that%20Christians%20were%20tortured%2C%20and%20that%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20administration%20was%20deafening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jaranwala%20incident%20has%20happened%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20%5Bwhen%5D%20religious%20political%20parties%20are%20seeking%20funds%20and%20increasing%20their%20vote%20bank%2C%20said%20Jacob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20politics%20of%20Blasphemy%20in%20Pakistan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20only%20the%20first%20blasphemous%20case%20that%20has%20emerged%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacob%20said%20that%20in%202023%20so%20far%2C%20197%20people%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20blasphemy%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20Of%20these%2085%25%20were%20Muslims%20who%20belonged%20to%20perhaps%20other%20sects%3B%209%25%20were%20Ahmadis%2C%20and%204.4%25%20were%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Justice%2C%20there%20were%20104%20blasphemy%20cases%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Sindh%20(51)%2C%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20(28)%2C%20Balochistan%20(01)%2C%20and%20Azad%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(13).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20former%20dictator%2C%20General%20Zia-ul-Haq%2C%20had%20strengthened%20the%20blasphemy%20law%2C%20imposing%20stringent%20penalties%20for%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20Parliament%20introduced%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769073%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Criminal%20Law%20(Amendment)%20Law%2C%202023%2C%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20made%20revisions%20to%20the%20sensitive%20blasphemy%20law%2C%20consequently%20intensifying%20the%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20civil%20society%20and%20activists%2C%20who%20are%20concerned%20that%20it%20might%20exacerbate%20tensions%20among%20the%20citizens%20and%20religious%20minority%20groups%2C%20while%20empowering%20religious%20extremist%20factions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20reconcile%20with%20the%20neighbourhood%20in%20Jaranwala%20where%20they%20used%20to%20live%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jacob%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20state%20to%20heal%20the%20wounds%20of%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20directly%20affected%20by%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692291244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17222113%2Fimage-1229.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fpakistan-mobs-torch-churches-houses-of-christians-over-blasphemy-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A