sk%20of%20the%20350%20newly%20elected%20lawmakers%20will%20be%20to%20vote%20on%20a%20new%20speaker%20for%20the%20chamber%2C%20with%20acting%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20proposing%20a%20candidate%20from%20his%20Socialist%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspains-parliament-opens-with-catalan-separatists-in-focus%2Farticleshow%2F102811114.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspains-parliament-opens-with-catalan-separatists-in-focus%2Famp_articleshow%2F102811114.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspains-parliament-opens-with-catalan-separatists-in-focus%2Famp_articleshow%2F102811114.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22You%20Talk%20Of%20Providing%20Stable%20Government%20But...%5C%22%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar%20Attacks%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Thursday%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20pulling%20down%20democratically%20installed%20governments%20in%20states%20not%20ruled%20by%20it%20while%20talking%20about%20providing%20political%20stability%2C%20and%20said%20the%20policy%20of%20current%20rulers%20is%20to%20widen%20the%20rift%20in%20society%20using%20caste%2C%20religion%20and%20language%20as%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20'Swabhiman%20Rally'%20in%20Beed%2C%20the%20home%20district%20of%20rebel%20NCP%20leader%20and%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Dhananjay%20Munde%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20MLAs%20who%20won%20elections%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20later%20changed%20sides%20and%20aligned%20with%20the%20saffron%20outfit%20will%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson%20by%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20came%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20section%20of%20MLAs%20from%20his%20own%20party%20and%20those%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20NCP%20MLAs%20from%20Beed%20district%20in%20central%20Maharashtra%2C%20three%20have%20joined%20the%20rebel%20faction%20led%20by%20deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20including%20Dhananjay%20Munde.%20The%20fourth%20MLA%2C%20Sandip%20Kshirsagar%2C%20is%20in%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20founder%20slammed%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20have%20gone%20to%20Manipur%20and%20understood%20the%20pain%20of%20people%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state%20which%20has%20witnessed%20deadly%20ethnic%20clashes%20since%20early%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManipur%20is%20among%20those%20north-eastern%20states%20which%20share%20international%20borders.%20The%20policy%20of%20neighbouring%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20not%20good....we%20need%20to%20be%20cautious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20defence%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20said%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20large-scale%20violence%20and%20arson%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferences%20were%20created%20among%20villages%2C%20society...houses%20were%20set%20ablaze.%20When%20houses%20in%20Manipur%20were%20burning%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20should%20have%20visited%20the%20state.%20He%20talked%20about%20Manipur%20for%20just%20three%20minutes%20before%20the%20Monsoon%20session%20of%20Parliament%20started.%20Later%2C%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20he%20spoke%20on%20Manipur%20for%204%20to%205%20minutes.%20The%20PM%20didn't%20try%20to%20understand%20the%20pain%20of%20women%20from%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20PM%20Modi%20is%20following%20into%20the%20footsteps%20of%20his%20party%20colleague%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20by%20including%20a%20'mi%20punha%20yein'%20(I'll%20come%20back%20again)%20element%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFadnavis%20did%20not%20return%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20(after%202019%20assembly%20polls)%2C%20but%20came%20back%20at%20a%20lower%20position%20(as%20deputy%20CM%20in%20June%202022%20after%20fall%20of%20the%20MVA%20government).%20One%20wonders%20what%20will%20he%20(PM%20Modi)%20return%20as%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20during%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%2C%20had%20asserted%20that%20he%20will%20come%20back%20to%20the%20Red%20Fort%20to%20address%20the%20nation%20on%20August%2015%20next%20year%2C%20too%2C%20implying%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20alliance%20will%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20policy%20of%20the%20current%20rulers%20is%20to%20widen%20the%20wedge%20in%20society%20using%20caste%2C%20religion%20and%20language%20as%20tools.%20The%20government%20doesn't%20think%20about%20the%20welfare%20of%20people%20who%20are%20doing%20hard%20work.%26quot%3B%20The%20veteran%20politician%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20toppling%20duly%20elected%20governments%20in%20opposition-ruled%20states%20even%20as%20it%20talked%20out%20about%20providing%20a%20stable%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20talk%20of%20providing%20a%20stable%20government%20but%20break%20duly%20elected%20governments%20in%20states.%20Governments%20elected%20by%20people%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20were%20pulled%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20leader%20said%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20does%20not%20talk%20about%20important%20issues%2C%20including%20rise%20in%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20important%20issues%2C%20but%20the%20government%20doesn't%20talk%20about%20them.%20There%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20inflation...fuel%20prices.%20Prices%20of%20fertilizers%20have%20gone%20up.%20Agriculture%20is%20facing%20problems%20but%20the%20government%20doesn't%20care%20about%20the%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20Union%20agriculture%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%2C%20he%20alleged%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20being%20imprisoned%20without%20any%20valid%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20leaders%20are%20being%20put%20behind%20bars%20on%20flimsy%20grounds.%20If%20there%20is%20unity%2C%20it%20will%20not%20take%20much%20time%20to%20overthrow%20such%20a%20power%20(current%20government)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20death%20of%2018%20patients%20in%20a%20span%20of%2024%20hours%20last%20weekend%20in%20a%20civic-run%20hospital%20in%20Thane%20district%2C%20the%20political%20turn%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEighteen%20patients%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Thane%20recently%2C%20but%20the%20state%20government%20remained%20a%20mute%20spectator.%20We%20can%20see%20where%20the%20state%20is%20now%20heading%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20(82)%20claimed%20a%20prominent%20member%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20who%20has%20joined%20the%20state%20government%2C%20citing%20the%20advanced%20age%20of%20the%20NCP%20president%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20should%20think%20of%20a%20new%20leader%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20go%20with%20those%20in%20power%2C%20you%20are%20free%20to%20do%20so%2C%20but%20think%20about%20those%20who%20have%20given%20you%20something%20in%20life.%20If%20you%20don't%20do%20this%2C%20people%20will%20teach%20you%20a%20lesson%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%2C%20apparently%20targeting%20the%20rebel%20NCP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20rally%2C%20state%20NCP%20president%20Jayant%20Patil%20(Sharad%20Pawar%20group)%20said%20MLAs%20of%20ruling%20parties%20are%20taking%20our%20rallies%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20saying%20%26quot%3BHindus%20are%20in%20danger%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20in%20the%20government%20say%20this%20government%20is%20driven%20by%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20then%20how%20come%20Hindus%20are%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20state%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatil%20attacked%20the%20central%20government%20over%20the%20latest%20CAG%20(Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India)%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20says%20they%20have%20ended%20corruption.%20But%20the%20CAG%20has%20brought%20out%20seven%20scams%20of%20this%20government.%20The%20cost%20of%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20(between%20Delhi%20and%20Gurugram)%20has%20increased%20by%2014%20times%20as%20per%20the%20CAG%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Maharashtra%20ministers%20Rajesh%20Tope%2C%20Jitendra%20Awhad%20and%20Anil%20Deshmukh%2C%20and%20NCP%20MLA%20Rohit%20Pawar%2C%20the%20grandnephew%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20were%20prominent%20among%20those%20present%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692288660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F38m83f5o_sharad-pawar_625x300_03_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyou-talk-of-providing-stable-government-but-sharad-pawar-attacks-bjp-4306789%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20chi