0was%20missing%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccompleted%E2%80%9D%20version%20are%20around%20the%20same%20duration%20but%20this%20time%20the%20board%20has%20hacked%20all%20the%20clips%20and%20pictures%20of%20Wasim%20Akram%20and%20replaced%20them%20with%20Imran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricket%20fans%20are%20now%20asking%20and%20wondering%20on%20social%20media%20where%20has%20Wasim%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasim%20had%20on%20Tuesday%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20PCB%20completely%20overlooking%20the%20role%20of%20Imran%20in%20some%20of%20Pakistan%20cricket's%20most%20memorable%20and%20iconic%20moments.%20Pakistan's%20former%20captain%20Rashid%20Latif%20said%20the%20PCB%20explanation%20was%20hard%20to%20digest%20because%20the%20tribute%20video%20was%20modified%20after%20nearly%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20wasn't%20the%20mistake%20accepted%20and%20resolved%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20backlash%20started%20on%20social%20media%20and%20in%20the%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20PCB%20had%20a%20verified%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20account%20which%20meant%20it%20can%20upload%20clips%20and%20videos%20up%20to%207-8%20minutes%20duration%20and%20secondly%20there%20was%20no%20duration%20bar%20on%20Youtube%20as%20well%20for%20the%20PCB%20channel%20to%20upload%20longer%20videos.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20where%20does%20this%20duration%20problem%20come%20in%20for%20PCB%3F%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20cover%20up%20and%20save%20face%20but%20the%20PCB%20still%20needs%20to%20give%20answers%20as%20to%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20authorizing%2C%20making%2C%20approving%20and%20releasing%20the%20video%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20PCB%20also%20got%20mixed%20reactions%20after%20it%20uploaded%20a%20two%20and%20half%20minute%20video%20on%20Thursday%20trying%20to%20chronicle%20the%20journey%20of%20Pakistan%20in%20all%20the%20World%20Cups%20from%201975%20to%202019.%20The%20video%20i