the%20ministers%20should%20avoid%20blaming%20anyone%20else...%20It%20is%20time%20we%20all%20work%20together...%20When%20the%20time%20comes%20and%20we%20come%20out%20of%20the%20disaster%2C%20you%20bring%20the%20report.%20Why%20so%20much%20damage%2C%20what%20was%20the%20reason%2C%20why%20the%20rescue%20was%20delayed%3F%20Report%20on%20this%20can%20come%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20denied%20that%20he%20had%20made%20any%20comment%20blaming%20the%20migrant%20labourers%20from%20Bihar.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20from%20Bihar%20are%20%26quot%3Bjust%20like%20our%20brothers%26quot%3B%20and%20damage%20to%20buildings%20in%20the%20state%20after%20rains%20was%20%26quot%3Bfault%20of%20our%20structural%20engineering%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%20had%20earlier%20quoted%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bmigrant%20architects%20(masons)%20whom%20I%20call%20'Bihari%20architects'%20come%20here%20and%20construct%20floor%20on%20floor%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20say%20anything%20as%20such.%20The%20people%20of%20Bihar%20were%20also%20stuck%20here.%20I%20got%20them%20evacuated%20by%20helicopters.%20Around%20200%20people%20from%20Bihar%20are%20still%20stuck%20here.%20They%20are%20like%20our%20brothers.%20It%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20our%20structural%20engineering%2C%20they%20are%20just%20labourers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20now%20told%20ANI.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20made%20arrangements%20to%20rescue%20Bihari%20labourers%20when%20they%20were%20stranded%20due%20to%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692287940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fnbufibp_shimla-house-collapse-650_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-slams-himachal-chief-minister-over-remark-on-bihar