three%20spinners.%20Shastri%20said%20even%20four%20spinners%20can%20be%20an%20option%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20the%20fourth%20one.%20Prasad%20on%20his%20part%20advocated%20the%20inclusion%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Shastri%20disagreed.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20fancy%20my%20thing%20for%20Ashwin's%20inclusion.%20Because%20you%20are%20playing%20in%20Asian%20conditions.%20He%20is%20one%20guy%20who%20can%20be%20effective%20against%20left-hand%20batters.%20Australia%20is%20filled%20with%20left-hand%20batters.%20We%20have%20seen%20that.%20Ashwin%20will%20be%20useful%20He%20is%20in%20best%20state%20of%20mind.%20He%20is%20at%20the%20right%20age.%20Especially%2C%20if%20we%20are%20plating%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20MSK%20Prasad%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fcricket-videos%2Fis-r-ashwin-still-in-the-reckoning-for-india-in-the-asia-cup-1392910%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPNCricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20thing%20is%20running%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20is%20the%20experience%20of%20Ashwin.%20It%20can%20be%20handy.%20Do%20you%20require%20two%20wrist%20spinners%3F%20That%20is%20one%20area%20which%20I%20am%20thinking.%20Jadeja%2C%20Chahal%20and%20even%20Axar%20are%20of%20similar%20style....%20the%20ball%20going%20out...What%20about%20left-handers.%20If%20he%20misses%20out%20we%20will%20miss%20him.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20argument%2C%20Shastri%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20Kuldeep's%20job%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20left-handers.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBu