ri-drops-the-b-word-while-debating-indias-asia-cup-2023-spin-combination-with-ex-bcci-selector-4305627%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Majority%20Of%20Muslims%20In%20India%20Have%20Converted%20From%20Hinduism%5C%22%3A%20Ghulam%20Azad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDPAP%20chairman%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20said%20a%20majority%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20have%20converted%20from%20Hinduism%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20example%20of%20this%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20where%20a%20majority%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20converted%20to%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20religion%20should%20not%20used%20to%20get%20political%20mileage%2C%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20said%20whoever%20takes%20refuge%20in%20religion%20in%20politics%20is%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20BJP%20leader%20said%20some%20(Muslims)%20have%20come%20from%20outside%20and%20some%20have%20not.%20Nobody%20has%20come%20from%20outside%20or%20inside.%20Islam%20came%20to%20existence%20just%201%2C500%20years%20ago.%20Hindu%20religion%20is%20very%20old.%20Around%2010-20%20of%20them%20(Muslims)%20must%20have%20come%20from%20outside%2C%20some%20were%20there%20in%20the%20Mughal%20army%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Azad%20Party%20(DPAP)%20chief%20told%20a%20gathering%20in%20Doda%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20other%20Muslims%20converted%20from%20Hinduism%20in%20India.%20An%20example%20of%20this%20can%20be%20found%20in%20Kashmir.%20Who%20were%20the%20Muslims%20in%20Kashmir%20600%20years%20ago%3F%20All%20were%20Kashmiri%20Pandits.%20They%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20All%20are%20born%20into%20this%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20said%20that%20when%20Hindus%20die%2C%20they%20are%20cremated.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20burnt%20in%20different%20places.%20Their%20ashes%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20river%20which%20mixes%20the%20water%2C%20and%20we%20drink%20that%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLater%2C%20who%20sees%20that%20the%20water%20contains%20their%20burnt%20ashes%3F%20People%20drink%20that%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DPAP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%20Muslims'%20flesh%20and%20bones%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20nation's%20soil%2C%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%2C%20too%2C%20become%20a%20part%20of%20this%20land.%20Their%20flesh%20and%20their%20bones%20become%20a%20part%20of%20Bharat%20Mata's%20soil.%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20both%20merge%20into%20this%20land.%20What%20difference%20is%20there%20between%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20on%20the%20use%20of%20religion%20for%20votes%2C%20Gulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhoever%20takes%20refuge%20in%20religion%20in%20politics%20is%20weak.%20Religion%20should%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20vote%20bank%20in%20politics.%20Voting%20should%20not%20be%20based%20on%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20names.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692286080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2hoo62b4_ghulam-nabi-azad-ani_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajority-of-muslims-in-india-have-converted-from-hinduism-ghulam-nabi-azad-4306664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DPAP%20chairman%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20said%20a%20majority%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20have%20converted%20from%20Hinduism%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20example%20of%20this%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20where%20a%20majority%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20converted%20to%20Islam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmajority-of-muslims-in-india-