Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Odisha%20government%20put%20its%20August%2011%20order%20on%20hold%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fodisha-govt-presses-pause-order-doing-away-deemed-forest-tag-8895444%2F%5C%22%3Eanticipating%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20environmentalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20did%20criticise%20the%20government%20order%20when%20it%20became%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrerna%20Singh%20Bindra%2C%20a%20conservationist%20and%20former%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Board%20for%20Wildlife%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprernabindra%2Fstatus%2F1691199292797501440%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20the%20government%20saying%20the%20category%20of%20deemed%20forests%20was%20%E2%80%98removed%E2%80%99%20was%20in%20contradiction%20to%20an%20earlier%20guarantee%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchanges-to-forest-conservation-act-heres-what-an-internal-document-of-the-govt-reveals%5C%22%3Ehad%20clarified%20to%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20examining%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20that%20lands%20identified%20by%20state%20expert%20committees%20as%20deemed%20forests%20would%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20amended%20forest%20conservation%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Deemed%E2%80%99%20forests%20are%20those%20not%20recorded%20by%20governments%20as%20forests%2C%20but%20that%20satisfy%20the%20dictionary%20meaning%20of%20a%20forest%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%20any%20large%20area%20with%20significant%20tree%20cover%20and%20undergrowth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20concept%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F187366700%2F%5C%22%3E1996%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3EGodavarman%20judgment%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20made%20in%20a%20timber%20logging%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Odisha%20government%E2%80%99s%20order%20seemingly%20declaring%20the%20concept%20null%20raised%20worries%20that%20such%20lands%2C%20which%20experts%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fno-more-deemed-forests-says-odisha-government%2Farticle67198187.ece%5C%22%3Econstitute%20nearly%20half%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20forests%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20protected%20under%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Finterview-why-there-is-mistrust-about-proposed-changes-to-forest-conservation-law%5C%22%3EInterview%20%7C%20Why%20There%20Is%20Mistrust%20About%20Proposed%20Changes%20to%20Forest%20Conservation%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20the%20ministry%20know%20for%20a%20fact%20that%20all%20%5Bexpert%20committees%5D%20have%20recorded%20deemed%20forests%3F%20Was%20any%20ground-truthing%20%3Cem%3E(sic)%3C%2Fem%3E%20done%2C%20were%20cadastral%20surveys%20undertaken%20to%20record%20and%20demarcate%20such%20forests%20in%20the%20field%3F%E2%80%9D%20Bindra%20asked%20in%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDoes%20the%20ministry%20know%20for%20a%20fact%20that%20all%20SECs%20have%20recorded%20deemed%20forests%3F%20Was%20any%20ground-truthing%20done%2C%20were%20cadastral%20surveys%20undertaken%20to%20record%20and%20demarcate%20such%20forests%20in%20the%20field%3F%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKerala%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20more%20diligent%20states%2C%20they%20were%20not%206%2Fn%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20prerna%20sin