0led%20India%20in%20a%20Test%20match%20against%20England%20at%20Birmingham%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20injury%20takes%20time%20to%20heal%2C%20it%20can%20be%20frustrating.%20Instead%20of%20having%20self%20doubt%2C%20I%20was%20thinking%20how%20to%20get%20fit%20and%20make%20a%20comeback.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20give%20the%20body%20time%20and%20respect.%20I%20never%20took%20it%20as%20a%20dark%20phase%20and%20thought%20my%20career%20could%20be%20over.%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20solutions%20and%20when%20solutions%20came%20I%20was%20feeling%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%20said%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20India's%20first%20T20I%20against%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20facing%20an%20injury%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20solve%20that%20problem%2C%20not%20what%20the%20world%20is%20saying.%20I%20wanted%20to%20recuperate.%20You%20learn%20to%20enjoy%20the%20game%20a%20lot%20more.%20I%20looked%20it%20as%20an%20off%20season.%20So%20I%20got%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20family.%20So%20was%20looking%20at%20the%20positives.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20missed%20being%20away%20from%20action.%26quot%3B%20Interactions%20with%20visiting%20teammates%20also%20kept%20him%20in%20good%20spirits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20time%20was%20needed%20for%20an%20injury%20to%20heal.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20met%20a%20lot%20of%20players%20at%20NCA.%20Sometimes%20things%20are%20not%20in%20your%20control.%20The%20body%20needs%20time%20to%20recover%20and%20you%20need%20to%20respect%2C%20%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20come%20back%20you%20have%20the%20hunger.%20When%20you%20are%20playing%20continuous%20cricket%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20an%20off%20season%20looks%20like.%20In%20this%20phase%2C%20as%20long%20as%20my%20physical%20restrictions%20were%20over%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20my%20fitness%20and%20bowling.%20I%20was%20following%20how%20the%20team%20was%20doing%20and%20(it)%20was%20good%20to%20