e%20Raj.%20The%20proportion%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20which%20participated%20in%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20might%20make%20us%20rethink%20the%20notion%20that%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism%20come%20naturally%20to%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20all%20of%20this%20be%20cited%20to%20say%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20desire%20for%20freedom%20was%20not%20legitimate%20or%20that%20even%20those%20who%20did%20not%20actively%20participate%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20liked%20their%20status%20of%20being%20colonial%20subjects%3F%20Everyone%20resented%20the%20fact%20that%20their%20will%20was%20not%20present%20in%20the%20rule%20they%20were%20under.%20The%20colonised%20Indians%20knew%20that%20they%20were%20treated%20by%20the%20rulers%20as%20lesser%20human%20beings%20and%20the%20price%20of%20getting%20benefits%20from%20the%20Raj%20was%20the%20surrender%20of%20the%20self.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tricolour%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20revolt%20against%20this%20subhuman%20condition.%20People%20took%20risks%20to%20hold%20it%2C%20unfurl%20it%2C%20and%20declare%20their%20autonomy.%20They%20endured%20caning%20and%20gunshots.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etiranga%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0represented%20that%20free%20spirit%20%E2%80%93%20defiance%20of%20the%20power%20that%20sought%20to%20subjugate%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tricolour%20also%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20togetherness%2C%20a%20new%20sociality%20that%20India%20wanted%20to%20forge.%20Freedom%20can%20be%20imagined%20without%20togetherness%2C%20and%20togetherness%20is%20impossible%20without%20equality.%20Nehru%2C%20while%20presenting%20the%20tricolour%20to%20the%20constituent%20assembly%2C%20encapsulated%20the%20spirit%20behind%20it%20in%20his%20own%20poetic%20way%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6this%20flag%20that%20I%20have%20the%20honour%20to%20present%20to%20you%20is%20not%2C%20I%20hope%20and%20trust%2C%20a%20flag%20of%20empire%2C%20a%20flag%20of%20imperialism%20%E2%80%93%20a%20flag%20of%20domination%20over%20anybody%2C%20but%20a%20flag%20of%20freedom%20not%20only%20for%20ourselves%20but%20a%20symbol%20of%20freedom%20for%20all%20people%20who%20may%20see%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-is-not-well-in-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EAll%20Is%20Not%20Well%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20India%20is%20not%20an%20empire%3B%20we%20are%20not%20annexing%20any%20foreign%20territory.%20However%2C%20the%20ambitions%20and%20ways%20of%20those%20who%20rule%20India%20can%20sometimes%20be%20imperialistic.%20When%20we%20force%20an%20unwilling%20hand%20to%20lift%20the%20flag%2C%20we%20subjugate%20them%2C%20dominate%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20an%20individual%20or%20organisation%20does%20not%20want%20to%20hold%20the%20tricolour%2C%20they%20should%20not%20be%20forced%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%20in%20its%20post-1947%20history%2C%20refused%20to%20hoist%20the%20tiranga%20at%20its%20offices%20on%20January%2026%20or%20August%2015.%20Were%20they%20ever%20forced%20to%20put%20up%20the%20tricolour%3F%20The%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20and%20members%20enjoyed%20all%20the%20rights%20that%20other%20citizens%20of%20India%20had%2C%20without%20being%20asked%20to%20march%20with%20the%20tricolour%20in%20their%20hands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20as%20the%20tricolour%20did%20not%20carry%20the%20same%20symbolism%20and%20message%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20same%20is%20arguably%20true%20of%20the%20present.%20The%20relationship%20of%20people%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20nation-state%20has%20been%20complex%20and%20has%20evolved%20over%20the%20last%2070%20years.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20making%20of%20the%20Indian%20nation%2C%20even%20after%20the%20departure%20of%20the%20British%2C%20has%20not%20always%20been%20pleasant%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20acknowledged%20in%20parliament%20when%20he%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20for%20using%20the%20Air%20Force%20against%20separatists%20in%20Mizoram%20in%201966.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20those%20who%20gave%20India%20its%20constitution%20wanted%20the%20tricolour%20to%20carry%20a%20message%20of%20friendship.%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitutionofindia.net%2Fdebates%2F22-jul-1947%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENehru%E2%80%99s%20words%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwherever%20it%20may%20go%2C%20it%20will%20bring%20a%20message%2C%20I%20hope%2C%20of%20freedom%20to%20those%20people%2C%20a%20message%20of%20comradeship%2C%20a%20message%20that%20India%20wants%20to%20be%20friends%20with%20every%20country%20of%20the%20world%20and%20India%20wants%20to%20help%20any%20people%20who%20seek%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fundamental%20idea%20behind%20the%20tricolour%20was%20that%20of%20freedom%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6That%20I%20hope%20will%20be%20the%20message%20of%20this%20Flag%20everywhere%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20that%20in%20the%20freedom%20that%20is%20coming%20to%20us%2C%20we%20will%20not%20do%20what%20many%20other%20people%20or%20some%20other%20people%20have%20unfortunately%20done%2C%20that%20is%2C%20in%20newfound%20strength%20suddenly%20expand%20and%20become%20imperialistic%20in%20design.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20thought%20behind%20this%20national%20flag%20was%20that%20we%20would%20not%20do%20to%20others%20what%20the%20British%20had%20done%20to%20us.%20Nehru%20and%20others%20knew%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20very%20special%20about%20us%20that%20can%20prevent%20us%20from%20lashing%20out%20at%20other%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-without-elected-government-five-years%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20In%205%20Years%20Without%20Elected%20Govt%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Crown%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20Has%20Become%20a%20Khap%20Panchayat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENehru%20said%2C%20and%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20agreed%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20that%20happened%2C%20that%20would%20be%20a%20terrible%20ending%20to%20our%20struggle%20for%20freedom.%20But%20there%20is%20that%20danger%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20I%20venture%20to%20remind%20this%20house%20of%20it%E2%80%A6%20there%20is%20this%20danger%20in%20a%20country%20suddenly%20unshackled%2C%20stretching%20out%20its%20arms%20and%20legs%20and%20trying%20to%20hit%20out%20at%20other%20people.%20And%20if%20we%20do%20that%2C%20we%20become%20just%20like%20other%20nations%20who%20seem%20to%20live%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20succession%20of%20conflicts%20and%20preparation%20for%20conflict.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201947%2C%20Kashmir%20chose%20to%20associate%20with%20India%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20its%20own%20identity%20and%20India%20accepted%20its%20accession%20on%20those%20terms.%20That%20compact%20was%20obliterated%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%20when%20Article%20370%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20parliament.%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20flag%20was%20snatched%20from%20its%20hands%2C%20and%20it%20was%20asked%20to%20hold%20only%20the%20tricolour.%20Now%2C%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20Nehru%20and%20the%20members%20of%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20had%20forbidden%20us%20to%20do.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20honest%20about%20the%20move.%20It%20was%20to%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Muslim%20Kashmiris%20and%20humiliate%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20images%20of%20Kashmiris%20queuing%20up%20to%20enter%20a%20stadium%20to%20watch%20the%20unfurling%20of%20the%20tricolour%20should%20not%20mislead%20us%20into%20thinking%20that%20they%20were%20doing%20so%20willingly%20and%20with%20joy%20in%20their%20hearts.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20tricolour%20represents%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20Indian%20state.%20They%20feel%20it%20has%20been%20planted%20on%20their%20chests%2C%20and%20their%20mouths%20have%20been%20forced%20shut.%20Journalists%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20live%20in%20fear%20of%20being%20charged%20with%20imaginary%20crimes.%20Dozens%20have%20had%20their%20passports%20impounded%20for%20no%20reason.%20You%20can%20imagine%20the%20state%20of%20those%20who%20want%20to%20hold%20a%20demonstration%20or%20even%20a%20hall%20meeting%20to%20criticize%20or%20protest%20a%20government%20decision.%20Kashmiri%20lips%20have%20been%20sealed%2C%20and%20hands%20tied%20behind%20their%20backs.%20And%20only%20then%20have%20they%20been%20allowed%20to%20walk%20freely.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20controlled%20places%20on%20Earth.%20All%20aspects%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20are%20being%20watched%20by%20the%20state.%20Academics%20cannot%20write%2C%20cannot%20speak.%20Their%20writings%2C%20their%20classes%2C%20their%20pasts%20are%20under%20observation%20and%20scrutiny.%20They%20can%20be%20fired%20from%20their%20jobs%20without%20any%20notice.%20University%20teachers%20are%20revisiting%20their%20academic%20papers%2C%20writings%2C%20and%20getting%20those%20pulled%20down%20from%20the%20websites%20which%20the%20Indian%20state%20might%20find%20objectionable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20colleague%20who%20was%20visiting%20a%20university%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20attend%20a%20seminar%20was%20taken%20aback%20when%20she%20saw%20the%20police%20marching%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall.%20If%20we%20think%20that%20in%20this%20atmosphere%20people%20can%20speak%20freely%2C%20there%20is%20something%20fundamentally%20wrong%20with%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-ca