20to%20Islam.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20phrase%20love%20jihad%20appeared%20first%20time%20as%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20in%202009%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatan%20Prabhat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Janajagruti%20Samiti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20was%20later%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad.%20It%20became%20a%20central%20agenda%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20governments%20in%20various%20states%20after%202014.%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20are%20among%20the%20prominent%20states%20that%20have%20such%20a%20law.%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20law%20mandates%20couples%20to%20declare%20religion%20and%20income.%20While%20occasional%20media%20reports%20bring%20out%20such%20marriages%20and%20the%20controversy%20they%20go%20through%2C%20there%20is%20no%20precise%20figure%20on%20the%20number%20of%20such%20cases.%20Hindu%20vigilante%20groups%20on%20prowl%20coupled%20with%20a%20biased%20and%20partisan%20police%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20arrests%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20%E2%80%98jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20an%20Islamic%20concept%2C%20love%20jihad%20obviously%20securitizes%20marriage%20between%20a%20Muslim%20male%20and%20women%20of%20Hindu%20(primarily)%20and%20other%20religions%20as%20jihad.%20Apparently%2C%20the%20motive%20behind%20coining%20this%20term%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20patriarchal%20and%20majoritarian%20Hindutva%20project%2C%20is%20to%20declare%20jihad%20as%20an%20aggressive%20ongoing%20struggle%20for%20both%20superiority%20and%20conversion.%C2%A0%20Joined%20with%20%E2%80%98love%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20is%20being%20portrayed%20as%20a%20religio-cultural%20and%20demographic%20offensive%20against%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20look%20at%20the%20concept%20of%20jihad%20in%20the%20holy%20Quran%20does%20not%20convey%20force%2C%20offensive%2C%20aggression%20or%20violence.%20Since%20there%20are%20approximately%2041%20verses%20out%20of%20total%206%2C236%20that%20mention%20jihad%20and%20its%20derivatives%20in%20the%20holy%20book%2C%20its%20multiple%20uses%2C%20implications%20and%20polysemy%20are%20apparent.%20There%20are%20also%20differences%20in%20Mecca%20and%20Medina%20verses.%20The%20Mecca%20verses%20emphasise%2C%20in%20fourteen%20verses%2C%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egeneral%20sense%20of%20a%20lifelong%20discipline%20to%20be%20adopted%20much%20more%20according%20to%20Islamic%20traditions.%20The%20Medina%20verses%20stress%20upon%20a%20sense%20of%20fighting.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20holy%20book%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20believers%20are%20only%20the%20ones%20who%20have%20believed%20in%20Allah%20and%20His%20Messenger%20and%20then%20doubt%20not%20but%20strive%20with%20their%20properties%20and%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20cause%20of%20Allah.%20It%20is%20those%20who%20are%20the%20truthful%E2%80%99%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EQuran%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2049%3A15).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Flies-insistence-and-disregard-for-evidence-the-journey-of-love-jihad-laws%5C%22%3ELies%2C%20Insistence%20and%20Disregard%20for%20Evidence%3A%20The%20Journey%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Laws%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20verses%20on%20jihad%20are%20not%20related%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20either%20war%20or%20violence.%20The%20technical%20word%20used%20for%20fighting%20is%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eqital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Cspan%3EJihad%20in%20its%20general%20meaning%20refers%20to%20the%20obligation%20on%20all%20Muslims%20to%20follow%20and%20realise%20God%E2%80%99s%20will%20to%20lead%20a%20life%20of%20virtue%20and%20to%20expand%20the%20teachings%20of%20Islam%20through%20preaching%2C%20education%2C%20example%2C%20writing%2C%20etc.%20Jihad%20also%20includes%20the%20right%20and%20the%20obligation%2C%20to%20defend%20Islam%20and%20the%20community%20from%20aggression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20indiscriminate%20use%20of%20the%20term%20by%20Muslim%20extremists%20and%20some%20Muslim%20nations%2C%20that%20have%20displayed%20aggressive%20intentions%20and%20politics%2C%20have%20created%20the%20impression%20for%20common%20non-Muslim%20people%20of%20the%20world%20that%20jihad%20is%20a%20war.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20sense%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20forces%20have%20used%20and%20projected%20jihad%20to%20the%20common%20gullible%20people%2C%20who%20know%20little%20beyond%20a%20ritualistic%20meaning%20about%20their%20own%20religion.%20The%20fear%20is%20thus%20easy%20to%20spawn.%20The%20Muslim%20militants%20have%20not%20helped%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20own%20religion.%20No%20wonder%20reactions%20to%20interfaith%20marriage%20between%20a%20Hindu%20girl%20and%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20are%20sharp%20and%20violent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sociological%20significance%20of%20love%20jihad%20is%20in%20its%20patriarchal%20manifestation.%20For%2C%20%E2%80%98love%E2%80%99%20is%20prefixed%20with%20jihad%20only%20when%20the%20bride%20is%20a%20Hindu%20and%20groom%20a%20Muslim.%20This%20concept%20is%20not%20used%20in%20a%20reverse%20situation%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20bride%20changes%20her%20faith.%20In%20case%20of%20a%20bride%20converting%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20it%20is%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghar%20wapasi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(home%20coming).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20in%20the%20frenzy%20and%20zeal%20to%20%E2%80%98protect%E2%80%99%20Hindu%20girls%20from%20the%20evil%20prowling%20Muslim%20eyes%2C%20not%20only%20the%20vigilante%20justice%2C%20but%20the%20full%20force%20of%20the%20state%20is%20turned%20on%20them%2C%20going%20beyond%20even%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20law.%20Perhaps%20because%20women%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%98property%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20traditional%20Hindu%20household.%C2%A0Most%20feminists%20within%20the%20Hindutva%20fold%20have%20never%20raised%20this%20point%20as%20patriarchy%20surrounding%20families%20takes%20upon%20itself%20the%20role%20of%20being%20the%20guardian.%20Both%2C%20the%20family%20and%20the%20society%2C%20arrogate%20to%20themselves%20the%20right%20to%20decide%20matches%20and%20what%20is%20good%20for%20a%20girl%20in%20matrimonial%20alliance.%E2%80%99Love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20seen%20and%20spoken%20about%20as%20a%20conspiracy%20in%20which%20conversion%20is%20the%20ultimate%20aim%20of%20Muslim%20men.%20This%20bogey%20also%20assumes%20that%20Hindu%20girls%20are%20victims%20because%20they%20have%20been%20coerced%20into%20converting.%20The%20same%20dynamics%20and%20logic%20work%20in%20the%20case%20of%20marriage%20between%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20girl%20and%20a%20Dalit%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConstitutionally%2C%20no%20Indian%20citizen%20can%20be%20prevented%20from%20exercising%20her%2Fhis%20matrimonial%20choice.%20Since%20the%20framers%20of%20the%20constitution%20did%20not%20foresee%20a%20situation%20of%20inter-faith%20marriages%20being%20objected%20to%2C%20and%20jihad%20being%20invoked%20in%20case%20of%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20marriage%2C%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20clause%20dealing%20with%20it.%20However%2C%20Articles%2015%2C%20Article%2025%20and%20others%20relating%20to%20free%20practice%20of%20religion%20provide%20guarantees%20to%20women%20and%20men%20of%20any%20religion%20to%20seek%20inter-faith%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-paper-and-at-odds-with-love-jihad-law-uttarakhands-interfaith-marriage-scheme-still-exists%5C%22%3EOn%20Paper%20and%20At%20Odds%20With%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Law%2C%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Interfaith%20Marriage%20Scheme%20Still%20Exists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20brings%20under%20question%20the%20anti-love%20jihad%20laws%20passed%20by%20states.%20The%20twist%20of%20the%20regimes%2C%20mostly%20headed%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20lies%20in%20%E2%80%98fraudulent%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98forced%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98by%20lure%E2%80%99%20conversions.%20Even%20though%20such%20charges%20are%20not%20easy%20to%20prove%2C%20local%20courts%20have%20been%20pliant%20towards%20the%20government%20and%20their%20police.%20While%20a%20large%20number%20of%20conversions%20have%20not%20been%20reported%2C%20UP%20has%20seen%20conviction%20under%20love-jihad%20laws.%20This%20violates%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20personal%20autonomy%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20the%20apex%20judiciary%20is%20not%20impressed%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20love%20jihad%20and%20the%20laws%20passed%20against%20it.%20A%20major%20test%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3ES%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ehafin%20Jahan%20v.%20Ashokan%20K.M%3C%2Fem%3E.%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20case%20in%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20reversed%20a%20ruling%20in%20favour%20of%20love%20jihad%20issued%20by%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20in%202018.%20In%202021%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Biren%20Vaishnav%20ruled%20that%2C%20%E2%80%98Prima-facie%20inter-faith%20marriages%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults%20by%20operation%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20Section%203%20of%20the%202003%20Act%20interferes%20with%20the%20intricacies%20of%20marriage%20including%20the%20right%20to%20the%20choice%20of%20an%20individual%2C%20thereby%20infringing%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20taken%20a%20strict%20view%20of%20the%20matter%20nor%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20cognizance%20of%20the%20unconstitutionality%20of%20the%20love%20jihad%20laws%20and%20declared%20any%20such%20law%20by%20any%20state%20%3Cem%3Eultra%20vires%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20states%20must%20desist.%20Neither%20the%20number%20of%20inter-faith%20marriages%2C%20nor%20India%E2%80%99s%20demography%20indicate%20any%20danger%20from%20such%20matrimonial%20alliances.%20This%20%E2%80%98otherisation%E2%80%99%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20minority%20must%20stop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20is%20a%20political%20scientist.%20He%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21%20and%20Principal%2C%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Evening%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%20(2018).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692268588000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17160453%2Fc6e7db8f-74ee-43fd-8bc8-583eba8ef9ff.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20majority%20of%20the%20verses%20in%20the%20Quran%20on%20jihad%20are%20not%20related%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20either%20war%20or%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20verification%20of%20SIM%20dealers%20mandatory%20to%20curb%20frauds%3A%20Vaishnaw%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692267612000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F11%2Ffull%2F1691771085-7669.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-verification-of-sim-dealers-mandatory-bulk-selling-halted-minister-123081700429_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20government%20has%20disconnected%2052%20lakh%20mobile%20connections.%20While%2067%2C000%20dealers%20have%20been%20blacklisted%2C%20300%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20SIM%20card%20dealers%20since%20May%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-verification-of-sim-dealers-mandatory-bulk-selling-halted-minister-123081700429_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-verification-of-sim-dealers-mandatory-bulk-selling-halted-minister-123081700429_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fpolice-verification-of-sim-dealers-mandatory-bulk-selling-halted-minister-123081700429_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Petition%20in%20the%20SC%20Brings%20Out%20Scale%20of%20Violence%20Against%20Women%20in%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12082107%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.18.56.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20Women%20in%20Governance%2C%20India%20(WGI)%20received%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20WGI%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20answers%20from%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20regarding%20incidents%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20during%20the%20Meitei-Kuki%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20have%20killed%20150%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20that%20the%20petition%20tried%20to%20raise%20was%20that%20since%20the%20clashes%20broke%20out%2C%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20the%20violence%2C%20restore%20peace%20and%20ensure%20protection%20of%20life%20and%20properties%20of%20citizens%20in%20the%20strife%20torn%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20by%20WGI%20has%20also%20argued%20that%20in%20this%20ongoing%20ethnic%20violence%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20of%20targeted%20sexual%20violence%20directed%20against%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%2C%20particularly%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20women%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20video%20of%20three%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20went%20viral%2C%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-video-arrest-biren-singh-supreme-court%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%98100s%20of%20such%20cases%E2%80%99%20all-around%20Manipur%2C%20where%20women%20were%20being%20harassed%20and%20raped.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20not%20say%20what%20precisely%20his%20government%20was%20doing%20to%20ensure%20justice%20in%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2031%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20provide%20a%20complete%20break-up%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUpdated-status-report-on-WPC-No.-540-and-connected-cases-before-SC.pdf%5C%22%3E5995%20First%20Information%20Reports%20%5BFIRs%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20the%20Manipur%20government%20claimed%20to%20have%20registered%20during%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20the%20State%2C%C2%A0including%20cases%20of%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20arson%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20burning%20of%20villages%2C%20homes%20and%20places%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20July%204%2C%20the%20petition%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20violence%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20approximately%20142%20people%20and%20the%20displacement%20of%20approximately%2055%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Who%20Gains%20and%20Who%20Loses%3F%20A%20Report%20From%20Manipur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-gains-and-who-loses-a-report-from-manipur%5C%22%3EWho%20Gains%20and%20Who%20Loses%3F%20A%20Report%20From%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20report%20presented%20in%20court%20also%20mentions%20the%20viral%20video%20case%20%E2%80%93%20stating%20that%20the%20two%20women%20were%20gang-raped%20and%20their%20father%20and%20brother%20were%20killed%20by%20a%20mob%20on%20May%204.%20While%20the%20Zero%20FIR%20in%20this%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20May%2018%20%E2%80%93%2014%20days%20after%20the%20incident%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20only%20on%20July%2024%20that%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20statements%20were%20recorded%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%E2%80%99s%20General%20Secretary%20and%20CPI%20leader%20Annie%20Raja%2C%20who%20was%20also%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98fact-finding%20committee%E2%80%99%20to%20probe%20the%20ground%20reality%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20violence%20and%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%2C%20had%20the%20government%20intervened%20on%20time.%20%E2%80%9COur%20report%20also%20clearly%20spells%20that%20the%20government%20had%20an%20agenda%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%20to%20pit%20the%20two%20communities%20at%20loggerheads%20so%20that%20they%20refuse%20to%20coexist.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20we%20could%20see%20that%20Meitei%20women%20themselves%20had%20become%20part%20of%20the%20crimes%20against%20Kuki%20women%2C%20alongside%20men.%20It%20is%20a%20major%20failure%20of%20the%20government%20which%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20brutality%20Kuki%20women%20have%20experienced%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raja%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20review%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20status%20report%20and%20the%20writ%20petition%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20about%20the%20gravity%20of%20crimes%20that%20women%20have%20faced%20during%20the%20three-month-long%20and%20continuing%20ethnic%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20report%20discloses%20several%20cases%20where%20women%20have%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20several%20cases%20mentioned%2C%20in%20a%20case%20of%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20of%20two%20women%20in%20Imphal%20East%20on%20May%204%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20arrest%20till%20date%3B%20nor%20has%20there%20been%20any%20detention%20in%20another%20case%20of%20gang-rape%20where%20an%2018-year-old%20woman%20came%20forward%20to%20narrate%20the%20ordeal%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%20at%20the%20Kangpokpi%20police%20station%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20described%20how%20she%20was%20first%20abducted%20and%20assaulted%20by%20four%20men%20in%20Imphal%20East%20on%20May%2015.%20According%20to%20the%20status%20report%2C%20three%20men%20raped%20her%20there.%20In%20her%20complaint%20filed%20at%20the%20Kangpokpi%20Police%20Station%2C%20she%20has%20detailed%20how%20she%20was%20abducted%20and%20tortured%20by%20at%20least%204-5%20men%20who%20hit%20with%20the%20butt%20of%20their%20guns.%20They%20issued%20multiple%20threats%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%20while%20scouting%20for%20a%20location%20to%20kill%20her.%20She%20begged%20them%20to%20spare%20her%20and%20promised%20the%20men%20that%20she%20will%20never%20return%20to%20Imphal%20if%20they%20let%20her%20go%20and%20she%20just%20wants%20to%20meet%20her%20parents.%20She%20was%20later%20dragged%20out%20of%20the%20car%2C%20physically%20assaulted%20and%20gang%20raped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20P.S.%20Kangpokpi%20on%20July%2021%2C%20pursuant%20to%20which%20a%20Zero%20FIR%20was%20registered%20on%2021.07.2023%20under%20Secs.%20376%3B%20376D%3B%20354%3B%20307%3B%20364%3B%20506%3B%2043%20IPC%20and%20Sec%203%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%20However%2C%20the%20petition%20claims%20that%20she%20has%20not%20been%20contacted%20by%20the%20police%20and%20has%20received%20no%20updates%20on%20the%20investigation%20or%20arrests.%20She%20has%20also%20not%20received%20any%20compensation%20from%20the%20government.%20She%20is%20currently%20staying%20at%20the%20Leicob%20relief%20camp%20with%20her%20family.%20She%20is%20very%20weak%2C%20traumatised%20and%20requires%20psychological%20counselling.%20The%20family%20also%20requires%20urgent%20rehabilitation%20since%20their%20house%20in%20Imphal%20was%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20case%2C%20two%20Kuki-Zo%20women%20who%20were%20out%20on%20May%204%20for%20work%20lost%20contact%20with%20their%20families%20later%20in%20the%20afternoon%20and%20could%20not%20be%20contacted%20later.%20Later%2C%20the%20family%20of%20these%20women%20learnt%20from%20a%20medical%20staffer%20that%20the%20two%20women%20aged%2024%20and%2021%20were%20gangraped%20allegedly%20by%20a%20Meitei%20mob.%20The%20family%20also%20learnt%20from%20a%20co-worker%20of%20these%20women%20that%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20100%20Meitei%20men%2C%20who%20came%20to%20their%20place%20of%20work%2C%20demanding%20to%20know%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20two%20Kuki-Zo%20women%20who%20worked%20there.%20The%20two%20women%20were%20dragged%20into%20a%20room%20where%20for%20almost%20two%20hours%20they%20were%20tortured%2C%20raped%20and%20subsequently%20murdered%20by%20the%20mob%20of%20Meiti%20men.%20While%20they%20have%20heard%20unverified%20reports%20that%20a%20postmortem%20has%20been%20conducted%2C%20no%20government%20official%20has%20contacted%20them%20to%20provide%20clear%20and%20accurate%20information.%20The%20informational%20vacuum%20that%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20living%20in%20has%20intensified%20their%20anguish%20and%20despair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20situations%20of%20conflict%20exacerbate%20and%20amplify%20the%20gender-based%20violence%20faced%20by%20women%20as%20their%20bodies%20are%20perceived%20as%20repositories%20of%20community%20%E2%80%9Chonour%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20well%20documented.%20In%20the%20present%20situation%2C%20women%20from%20the%20minority%2C%20tribal%20and%20marginalised%20Kuki-Zo%20community%2C%20viewed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D%2C%20were%20targeted%20by%20mobs%20of%20the%20dominant%20community%2C%20the%20petition%20has%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%2C%20WGI%2C%20founded%20in%202009%2C%20is%20a%20network%20of%20academics%2C%20social%20workers%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20activists%20who%20have%20been%20engaging%20actively%20on%20issues%20impacting%20the%20lives%20of%20women%2C%20more%20particularly%20the%20security%20of%20women%20in%20the%20conflict%20prone%20regions%20in%20the%20states%20of%20North%20East%20and%20strengthening%20the%20capacity%20of%20grassroot%20women%20leaders%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20empowering%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continuing%20violence%2C%20the%20petition%20said%2C%20has%20taken%20a%20heavy%20toll%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20life%2C%20physical%20assaults%20and%20injuries%2C%20destruction%20of%20homes%20and%20property%2C%20internal%20displacement%20with%20many%20fleeing%20their%20villages%20and%20homes%20to%20save%20their%20lives%2C%20loss%20of%20livelihood%20and%20employment%2C%20disruption%20of%20health%20and%20education%20facilities%2C%20and%20a%20deep%20rupture%20in%20society%20along%20ethnic%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692266515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12082107%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.18.56.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fpetition-in-the-sc-brings-out-scale-of-violence-again