ed%20with%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20redefine%20Islam%20within%20an%20evolving%20global%20landscape%20of%20declining%20Muslim%20powers%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20European%20imperialism%20in%20the%20late%2019th%20and%20the%20early%2020th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20shines%20a%20spotlight%20on%20Jamal-ud-din%20Afghani%E2%80%99s%20thought-provoking%20perspective%20on%20the%20decline%20of%20the%20Islamic%20civilisation.%20Taking%20a%20stance%20that%20harboured%20optimism%2C%20he%20suggested%20that%20Muslims%20could%20draw%20inspiration%20from%20the%20rapid%20advancement%20of%20the%20Western%20world.%20Afghani%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20self-change%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Quranic%20verse%2C%20%E2%80%9CVerily%2C%20God%20does%20not%20change%20the%20state%20of%20the%20people%20until%20they%20change%20themselves%20inwardly%2C%E2%80%9D%20resonates%20with%20a%20transformative%20theme%20that%20courses%20through%20the%20works%20of%20all%20the%20scholars%20examined%20by%20Purohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scholars%E2%80%99%20collective%20response%20to%20the%20decline%20of%20Muslim%20powers%20and%20the%20concomitant%20need%20to%20redefine%20Islam%20in%20the%20face%20of%20colonial%20dominance%20underscores%20a%20common%20thread.%20As%20the%20Safavid%2C%20Mughal%20and%20Ottoman%20Empires%20crumbled%20and%20European%20powers%20expanded%20their%20reach%2C%20these%20thinkers%20sought%20to%20synthesise%20Islamic%20teachings%20with%20European%20ideas%20of%20education%2C%20science%2C%20and%20civilisational%20progress.%20Their%20quest%20was%20not%20to%20adopt%20European%20secularism%20in%20total%20but%20to%20reshape%20Islam%20in%20harmony%20with%20their%20evolving%20worldviews%2C%20all%20the%20while%20remaining%20loyal%20to%20their%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPurohit%E2%80%99s%20astute%20analysis%20uncovers%20a%20notable%20undercurrent%20within%20these%20reform%20efforts%3A%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20Sunni%20majoritarian%20perspective.%20While%20these%20modernist%20scholars%20championed%20unity%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20their%20vision%20often%20cast%20aside%20minority%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Shia%2C%20Bahai%2C%20Ahmadi%20and%20Ismaili%20communities.%20This%20paradoxical%20perspective%20simultaneously%20advocated%20inclusivity%20while%20sowing%20exclusivity%2C%20as%20those%20who%20did%20not%20align%20with%20their%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98authentic%E2%80%99%20Islam%20were%20denounced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%98Sunni%20normative%20bias%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20Purohit%20terms%20it%2C%20explicitly%20or%20implicitly%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20essential%20component%20of%20mainstream%20modernist%20thought%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20%E2%80%98insiders%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%20are%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20particularly%20intriguing%20aspect%20that%20%3Cem%3ESunni%20Chauvinism%20and%20the%20Roots%20of%20Muslim%20Modernism%3C%2Fem%3E%20underscores%20is%20the%20dual%20nature%20of%20these%20scholars%E2%80%99%20attitudes%20towards%20minority%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20they%20borrowed%20from%20the%20beliefs%20of%20these%20groups%20to%20strengthen%20their%20arguments%20%E2%80%93%20for%20instance%2C%20Afghani%20describes%20his%20own%20qualifications%20as%20a%20potential%20leader%20by%20appropriating%20and%20reworking%20ideas%20of%20prophecy%20that%20originate%20from%20the%20Shia%20and%20Bahai%20groups%20whom%20he%20accused%20of%20heresy.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20condemned%20the%20same%20minority%20groups%20as%20heretical.%20The%20juxtaposition%20of%20the%20scholars%E2%80%99%20contradictory%20views%20underscores%20the%20complexities%20within%20their%20reform%20endeavours%20and%20also%20illuminates%20the%20biases%20embedded%20within%20their%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20in%20point%20is%20the%20exploration%20of%20Iqbal%E2%80%99s%20worldview%20%E2%80%93%20his%20seemingly%20contradictory%20advocacy%20for%20Pakistan%20alongside%20his%20call%20for%20unity%20among%20Muslims.%20Purohit%E2%80%99s%20scrutiny%20sheds%20light%20on%20Iqbal%E2%80%99s%20nuanced%20vision%20and%20his%20attempt%20to%20reconcile%20the%20tensions%20between%20these%20two%20objectives.%20This%20facet%20of%20the%20book%20resonates%20with%20ongoing%20debates%20within%20Pakistan%20and%20beyond%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20delicate%20balance%20between%20national%20identity%20and%20religious%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20then%20turns%20to%20examining%20the%20journey%20from%20Muslim%20modernism%20to%20Islamism%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20Mawdudi.%20While%20the%20earlier%20modernists%20responded%20within%20the%20colonial%20context%2C%20the%20writings%20of%20Mawdudi%20emerged%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20India%20becoming%20a%20modern%20nation-state.%20His%20emphasis%20on%20establishing%20an%20Islamic%20state%20and%20his%20fervent%20writings%20against%20minority%20groups%20echo%20the%20fault-line%20in%20earlier%20modernist%20themes%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20different%20context.%20This%20evolution%20offers%20valuable%20insights%20into%20the%20contemporary%20rise%20of%20Islamism%20and%20its%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20high%20points%20of%20the%20book%20is%20its%20exploration%20of%20the%20evolution%20of%20Mawdudi%20and%20Syed%20Qutb%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20which%20indirectly%20inspired%20groups%20like%20Al%20Qaeda.%20Purohit%E2%80%99s%20careful%20analysis%20reveals%20how%20Syed%20Qutb%E2%80%99s%20binary%20view%20%E2%80%93%20of%20believers%20and%20infidels%20%E2%80%93%20resonates%20in%20Al%20Qaeda%E2%80%99s%20extremist%20worldview.%20A%20worldview%20which%20seeks%20to%20bring%20Muslim%20communities%20under%20a%20new%20Islamic%20state%2C%20it%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20horrific%20consequences%20that%20can%20arise%20when%20ideological%20interpretations%20take%20a%20radical%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17133811%2FScreen-Shot-2020-05-11-at-11.57.24-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22150%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22151%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETeena%20Purohit.%20Photo%3A%20Boston%20University%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%E2%80%99s%20relevance%20extends%20far%20beyond%20academia.%20It%20provides%20invaluable%20insights%20into%20the%20modern-day%20challenges%20confronting%20Muslim%20societies%20across%20the%20world.%20From%20the%20divisions%20arising%20due%20to%20Sunni%20normative%20bias%20to%20the%20persistence%20of%20exclusionary%20interpretations%20of%20Sunni%20Islam%2C%20these%20issues%20continue%20to%20shape%20the%20discourse%20and%20dynamics%20within%20Muslim%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20grappling%20with%20the%20complexities%20of%20identity%2C%20diversity%20and%20political%20turmoil%2C%20Purohit%E2%80%99s%20work%20offers%20a%20poignant%20reflection%20on%20the%20intricate%20relationship%20between%20religious%20interpretation%2C%20cultural%20context%20and%20the%20path%20to%20progress.%20As%20Muslim%20communities%20across%20the%20world%20navigate%20these%20contemporary%20challenges%2C%20comprehending%20the%20historical%20perspectives%20illuminated%20in%20this%20book%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20guiding%20light%20toward%20potential%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESunni%20Chauvinism%20and%20the%20Roots%20of%20Muslim%20Modernism%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20powerful%20reminder%20that%20the%20journey%20of%20reconciling%20tradition%20and%20modernity%20is%20ongoing%2C%20and%20that%20the%20lessons%20from%20history%20can%20illuminate%20the%20quest%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20harmonious%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaleem%20Rashid%20Shah%20is%20a%20literary%20critic%20and%20independent%20writer%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692260158000%2C%22visua