%20fallen%20sick%20from%20taking%20the%20cough%20syrup%20and%2018%20of%20them%20had%20died.%20It%20is%20unclear%20at%20the%20moment%20when%20these%20other%20deaths%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUzbekistan%20has%20put%2021%20people%20on%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%93%2020%20locals%20and%20one%20Indian%20%E2%80%93%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cough%20syrup%20in%20question%20is%20%E2%80%98Doc-1%20Max%E2%80%99%2C%20manufactured%20by%20the%20Noida-based%20company%20Marion%20Biotech.%20Three%20of%20the%20people%20on%20trial%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters%2C%20including%20the%20one%20Indian%2C%20work%20for%20Quramax%20Medical%2C%20a%20company%20that%20sold%20medicines%20manufactured%20by%20Marion%20Biotech%20in%20Uzbekistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuramax%20CEO%20Singh%20Raghvendra%20Pratar%20paid%20officials%20at%20the%20state%20centre%20for%20expertise%20and%20standardisation%20of%20medicinal%20products%20%2433%2C000%20so%20that%20they%20would%20skip%20a%20mandatory%20inspection%20of%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20products%2C%20state%20prosecutor%20Saidkarim%20Akilov%20has%20alleged.%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20this%20inspection%20involves%20testing%20in%20Uzbekistan%20or%20requests%20for%20tests%20to%20be%20done%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pratar%20denied%20the%20charges%20in%20court%2C%20he%20did%20say%20he%20gave%20the%20money%20cited%20to%20the%20officials%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20token%20of%20appreciation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeven%20of%20the%2021%20defendants%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20charges%20against%20them%2C%20which%20included%20tax%20evasion%2C%20sale%20of%20substandard%20or%20counterfeit%20medicines%2C%20abuse%20of%20office%2C%20negligence%2C%20forgery%2C%20and%20bribery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwh