-chief-minister-hemant-soren-threatens-legal-action-on-enforcement-directorate-for-summon%2Fcid%2F1959494%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fed-summons-jharkhand-cm-soren-again-in-yet-another-alleged-money-laundering-case%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20called%20for%20questioning%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20an%20alleged%20defence%20land%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20summons%20was%20issued%20to%20him%20on%20August%207.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20for%20the%20second%20time%20that%20Soren%20had%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20central%20agency%20in%20connection%20with%20money%20laundering%20cases%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20time.%20He%20had%20also%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20last%20November%20in%20connection%20with%20another%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20illegal%20mining%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%2C%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20summons%20and%20the%20day%20he%20was%20called%20in%20for%20questioning.%20%E2%80%9CYour%20choice%20of%20the%20date%20does%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20the%20undersigned%20%5BSoren%5D.%20You%20and%20your%20political%20masters%20are%20fully%20aware%20that%20being%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20undersigned%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hoist%20the%20National%20Flag%E2%80%A6.%20Preparations%20for%20the%20Independence%20Day%20function%20start%20a%20week%20before%20and%20August%2014%20is%20an%20important%20day%20for%20the%20same%20when%20many%20meetings%20are%20pre-scheduled%E2%80%A6.%20The%20captioned%20summons%E2%80%A6%20is%20deliberate%20and%20part%20of%20the%20design%20to%20besmirch%20the%20reputation%20not%20only%20of%20the%20undersigned%20but%20also%20the%20elected%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soren%20said%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20he%20addressed%20to%20Deovrat%20Jha%2C%20ED%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Ranchi%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20warn%20the%20probe%20agency%20of%20legal%20action%20if%20summons%20issued%20to%20him%20is%20not%20withdrawn.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20undersigned%20calls%20upon%20you%20to%20forthwith%20withdraw%20the%20captioned%20summons%20failing%20which%2C%20the%20undersigned%20shall%20be%20constrained%20to%20seek%20legal%20remedies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20mincing%20words%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%E2%80%9D%20only%20because%20he%20does%20not%20align%20with%20the%20party%20ruling%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20central%20agencies%20have%20been%20targeting%20the%20undersigned%20for%20over%20a%20year%20now%20only%20because%20the%20undersigned%20is%20not%20aligned%20with%20the%20political%20party%20which%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20earlier%20summons%2C%20of%20November%202022%2C%20Soren%20notes%20that%20he%20has%20already%20provided%20details%20of%20all%20movable%20and%20immovable%20properties%20owned%20by%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members%20along%20with%20certified%20copies%20of%20the%20title%20deeds.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20has%20already%20furnished%20details%20of%20his%20bank%20account%20and%20permanent%20account%20number%20(PAN)%20number.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20he%20was%20questioned%20for%20over%2010%20hours%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20mining%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20also%20referred%20to%20an%20instance%20from%202020%20where%20the%20Lokpal%20directed%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20conduct%20an%20enquiry%20against%20his%20father%2C%20Shibu%20Soren%2C%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20filed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20such%20enquiry%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20wrongfully%20and%20illegally%20carried%20out%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20immovable%20assets%20owned%20by%20the%20undersigned.%20It%20may%20be%20in%20your%20interest%20to%20obtain%20a%20report%20from%20CBI%20on%20the%20undersigned%E2%80%99s%20immovable%20assets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2014%2C%20a%20person%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20regional%20office%20of%20the%20ED%20on%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20behalf%20and%20submitted%20a%20sealed%20envelope%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhemant-soren-skips-enforcement-directorates-summons-in-land-grabbing-case-2421308-2023-08-15%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692250377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17105007%2FF3jBZdiXEAA99Q2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwithdraw-summons-forthwith-jharkhand-cm-soren-warns-ed-of-legal-action%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20was%20asked%20to%20depose%20on%20August%2014%20at%20the%20central%20agency's%20office%20in%20Ranchi%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20which%20he%20gave%20it%20a%20miss.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwithdraw-summons-forthwith-jharkhand-cm-soren-warns-ed-of-legal-action%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JPMorgan%20index%20may%20include%20India's%20sovereign%20bonds%20in%202024%2C%20says%20Pictet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692241149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F17%2Ffull%2F1692241047-2927.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi