0-acre%20farmland%20in%20his%20hometown%20Kota%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20business%20to%20utilise%20the%20land%20for%20dairy%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20with%2C%20he%20completed%20a%20dairy%20science%20course%20from%20the%20National%20Dairy%20Research%20Institute%20(NDRI)%20in%202014%3B%20worked%20in%20companies%20like%20Mother%20Dairy%2C%20Amul%20and%20Nestle%3B%20and%20pursued%20a%20dairy%20automation%20course%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20University%20in%20Israel%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20end%20of%202015%2C%20I%20returned%20home.%20With%20the%20technical%20help%20from%20a%20milk%20company%20from%20Israel%2C%20we%20established%20a%20dairy%20farm%20on%20our%20land.%20We%20started%20with%20milk%20subscriptions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amanpreet%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20Gau%20Organics%20in%202016%20with%20his%20brothers%20Uttam%20Jyot%20and%20Gaganpreet.%20They%20bought%2027%20cows%20and%20started%20with%20milk%20subscriptions%2C%20later%20moving%20to%20value-added%20products%20like%20ghee%2C%20butter%2C%20organic%20jaggery%2C%20honey%2C%20sweets%2C%20etc.%20Today%2C%20they%20also%20sell%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure%2C%20alongside%20training%20other%20farmers%20in%20doing%20so%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20notable%20about%20Amanpreet%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20that%20they%20are%20also%20able%20to%20cover%2070%25%20of%20their%20electricity%20needs%20on%20their%20own.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20the%2032-year-old%20to%20understand%20how.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20the%20most%20out%20of%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNshc_H6es%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNshc_H6es%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNshc_H6es%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Gau%20Organics%E2%84%A2%20(%40gau.organics)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmanpreet%20realised%20early%20on%20that%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20rely%20on%20milk%20and%20would%20have%20to%20expand%20to%20value-added%20products.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20issue%20faced%20by%20dairy%20farmers%20is%20the%20complete%20reliance%20on%20milk%20for%20income.%20A%20cow%20produces%20milk%20after%20nine%20months%20of%20pregnancy.%20She%20is%20not%20a%20machine.%20If%20she%20has%20an%20upset%20stomach%2C%20the%20milk%20will%20not%20be%20good.%20We%20need%20to%20take%20all%20this%20into%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20another%20point%20that%20came%20to%20his%20notice%20was%20the%20excess%20waste%20generated%20by%20their%20livestock.%20So%20alongside%20selling%20value-added%20products%2C%20they%20started%20selling%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure%20on%20Amazon.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20listed%20cow%20dung%20and%20vermicompost%20manure%20in%202018%20on%20Amazon.%20We%20saw%20a%20pickup%20in%20sales%20only%20in%202020%20after%20the%20lockdown%20was%20announced.%20As%20people%20started%20gardening%20at%20home%2C%20sellers%20like%20us%20saw%20an%20uptick%20in%20sales.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20sales%20picked%20up%2C%20Amanpreet%20also%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255951%2Fhyderabad-sids-farm-iit-kharagpur-cow-cattle-earns-crores-milk-subscription-plan-dairy-revenue-kishore-indukuri-inspirational-success-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20to%20sell%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20farmers%20were%20dependent%20only%20on%20milk%20and%20were%20not%20given%20a%20good%20price%20for%20it.%20So%20we%20started%20training%20them%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20excreta%20from%20cows%2C%20make%20proper%20manure%2C%20and%20sell%20it.%20We%20trained%20over%2055%20farmers%2C%20mostly%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Amanpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20help%20farmers%20get%20a%20daily%20income%20by%20selling%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure.%20Female%20farmers%20are%20able%20to%20get%20Rs%20200-300%20per%20day%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E70%25%20of%20electricity%20is%20generated%20on%20the%20farm%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gau%20Organics%20sell%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgauu-1692019972-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m