22%3EThe%20harvested%20millets%20are%20processed%20at%20the%20factory%20after%20which%20they%20are%20turned%20into%20products%20like%20dosa%20mixes%20and%20malts%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Somashekar%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Hemadri%20Reddy%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Kodumur%20village%20has%20been%20cultivating%20brown%20top%20millet%20since%20his%20association%20with%20Adithi%20Millets%20in%20June%202022.%20Sharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20joining%20Adithi%20Millets%2C%20I%20would%20sow%20the%20seeds%20of%20brown%20top%20millet%20in%20four%20acres%20and%20get%204%2C000%20kg%20millets.%20When%20I%20would%20sell%20it%20in%20the%20market%2C%20I%20would%20get%20an%20MSP%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20quintal%20and%20earn%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20the%20entire%20harvest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20joining%20Adithi%20Millets%20the%20farmer%20adopted%20Somashekar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2F5-miracle-millets-that-helped-a-67-yo-control-her-diabetes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ere-cropping%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%20(leaving%20six%20inches%20of%20stubble%20in%20the%20ground%20after%20harvest%20and%20allowing%20it%20to%20grow%20in%20the%20monsoon%20without%20sowing%20new%20seeds).%20This%20gave%20him%20yet%20another%20harvest%20of%204%2C000%20kg%20of%20brown%20top%20millets%2C%20which%20he%20then%20sold%20for%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20almost%20double%20my%20previous%20revenue%20without%20sowing%20new%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomashekar%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20glad%20he%20can%20help%20his%20community.%20His%20beliefs%20in%20good%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20a%20love%20for%20farming%20have%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%20and%20helped%20him%20scale%20his%20empire%20to%20what%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C