switching%20buses%20and%20trains%2C%20he%20reached%20Varanasi%20%E2%80%94%20about%201%2C000%20km%20from%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20knowledge%20of%20how%20to%20go%20back%20home%2C%20the%20child%20stayed%20at%20the%20railway%20station%20and%20survived%20by%20begging.%20Meanwhile%2C%20his%20family%20back%20home%20went%20pillar%20to%20post%20in%20search%20of%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brother%20Raheed%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20did%20not%20come%20back%20home%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20barber%20shop%20and%20were%20informed%20that%20he%20never%20arrived%20there.%20He%20cannot%20speak%20clearly%20and%20is%20intellectually%20disabled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20registered%20missing%20report%20FIRs%20at%20several%20police%20stations.%20I%20went%20on%20my%20bike%20to%20a%20distance%20of%20up%20to%20130%20km%20to%20find%20him.%20We%20tried%20our%20best%20but%20we%20could%20not%20find%20him.%20We%20feared%20if%20he%20was%20even%20alive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20four%20years%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-4-1691757772.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Like%20Shoaib%2C%20730%20lost%20children%20in%20Varanasi%20have%20been%20reunited%20with%20their%20families%20since%20last%20July.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-4-1691757772.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-4-1691757772-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-4-1691757772-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet