Ignis%20is%20its%20use%20of%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20in%20inculcating%20these%20curricula%20and%20making%20learning%20fun%20for%20children.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-2-1691584721.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-2-1691584721-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-2-1691584721-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-2-1691584721-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-2-1691584721-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326822%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20Ignis%20is%20its%20use%20of%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20in%20inculcating%20these%20curricula%20and%20making%20learning%20fun%20for%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20he%20dropped%20out%20of%20JNU%20to%20start%20teaching%20life%20skills%20and%20grammar%20to%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20went%20to%20JNU%2C%20my%20parents%20expected%20me%20to%20be%20a%20professor%20somewhere%20but%20I%20realised%20I%20could%20do%20a%20lot%20better%20and%20bigger%20by%20teaching%20students.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20best%20education%20started%20after%20I%20left%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20he%20started%20teaching%20in%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Bengaluru.%20As%20part%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20smaller%20towns%20in%20the%20state%20for%20promotional%20programmes%2C%20he%20would%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20interact%20with%20school%20students.%20%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20I%20observed%20the%20horrible%20system%20of%20education%20we%20have.%20I%20asked%20the%20students%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20a%20cloud%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20