ons%20from%20people%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20I%20needed%20a%20concrete%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20purchase%20land%20and%20construct%20the%20sanctuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20daily%20cost%20of%20feeding%20the%20animals%20and%20upkeep%20of%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2018%2C000.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-2-1691587385-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20daily%20cost%20of%20feeding%20the%20animals%20and%20maintaining%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2018%2C000%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sai%20Vignesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20avenues%20and%20donations%2C%20Sai%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20ancestral%20home%20that%20belonged%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20determined%20to%20convince%20my%20parents%20to%20sell%20the%20house%20and%20help%20me%20with%20the%20funds.%20While%20it%20was%20a%20big%20decision%2C%20they%20could%20see%20that%20it%20was%20my%20only%20passion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20and%20his%20parents%20sold%20their%20ancestral%20home%20and%20purchased%20an%20eight-acre%20land%20near%20Poondi%20reservoir%20in%20T