0all%20these%20years.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20when%20I%20look%20back%20and%20see%20nature%20thriving%20in%20all%20its%20glory%20at%20the%20sanctuary%2C%20it%20fills%20me%20with%20indescribable%20joy%20and%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20you%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20who%20also%20works%20as%20a%20web%20developer%2C%20dedicates%20most%20of%20his%20income%20to%20the%20upkeep%20of%20the%20sanctuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20my%20income%2C%20there%20are%20people%20who%20keep%20donating%20regularly%20in%20kind%20and%20money.%20The%20per-day%20expense%20for%20the%20sanctuary%E2%80%99s%20upkeep%20and%20for%20feeding%20the%20animals%20comes%20to%20around%20Rs%2018%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20who%20wants%20to%20contribute%20can%20do%20it%20in%20any%20form.%20You%20can%20volunteer%20here%20as%20we%20are%20always%20short%20of%20hands%2C%20or%20you%20can%20also%20donate%20money%2C%20food%2C%20or%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20regularly%20shares%20updates%20on%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20well-being%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Sai%20is%20planning%20to%20build%20a%20quarantine%20centre%20in%20the%20sanctuary%20for%20animals%20with%20contagious%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20further%20his%20cause%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20Sai%20at%2089393%2020846.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691645042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-1-1691587222.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sai%20Vignesh%20(22)%20started%20helping%20animals%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20grandfather.%20Later%2C%20he%20started